---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="About — Bluesky Software" description="Bluesky Software is a design and engineering agency building premium digital platforms for businesses, clubs, and organisations.">

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container fade-in">
      <div class="surface soft pad-lg">
        <span class="kicker">About Bluesky</span>
        <h1 class="title">We build digital platforms that feel calm, clear, and high-trust.</h1>
        <p class="copy">
          Bluesky is a design and engineering agency focused on full-stack digital delivery.
          We combine brand-led website design, mobile app experiences, and integrated operational
          modules — so your organisation runs one beautiful, coherent platform instead of juggling
          a patchwork of disconnected tools.
        </p>
        <p class="copy">
          We believe your digital presence should feel like a clear day. No friction. No clutter.
          No complexity your team didn't ask for. Just clean, reliable software that works
          — and looks exceptional doing it.
        </p>
        <div class="stats">
          <span class="stat">Website + app delivery</span>
          <span class="stat">Integrated operations modules</span>
          <span class="stat">Built for long-term growth</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="section tight">
    <div class="container reveal">
      <div class="surface pad">
        <span class="kicker">What drives us</span>
        <h2 class="title">The principles behind every platform we build</h2>
        <p class="copy">
          These aren't wall decorations. They inform every design decision, every line of code,
          and every conversation we have with clients.
        </p>
        <div class="grid four">
          <article class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="3"/><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="23"/><line x1="4.22" y1="4.22" x2="5.64" y2="5.64"/><line x1="18.36" y1="18.36" x2="19.78" y2="19.78"/><line x1="1" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"/><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12"/><line x1="4.22" y1="19.78" x2="5.64" y2="18.36"/><line x1="18.36" y1="5.64" x2="19.78" y2="4.22"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Clarity by default</h3>
            <p>Every screen has one obvious goal. Every action has a clear path. No clutter, no confusion.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Premium craft</h3>
            <p>Our interfaces are intentionally designed, not assembled from templates. Every pixel earns its place.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 00.33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 010 2.83 2 2 0 01-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 00-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 01-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 009 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 01-2.83-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 004.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 010-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 004.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 00-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 012.83-2.83l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 009 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 001-1.51V3a2 2 0 014 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 001 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 001.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 012.83 2.83l-.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0019.4 9a1.65 1.65 0 001.51 1H21a2 2 0 010 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.51 1z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Operational thinking</h3>
            <p>We design around how your team actually works — not just how pages look in a mockup.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 007.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 00-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 00-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 007.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>True partnership</h3>
            <p>We're not a vendor you forget about after launch. We're your digital team — from day one, for the long run.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section class="section tight">
    <div class="container reveal">
      <div class="surface pad">
        <span class="kicker">Our approach</span>
        <h2 class="title">From the first conversation to ongoing growth</h2>
        <p class="copy">
          We handle every phase in-house — strategy, design, engineering, launch, and continuous improvement.
          One team, one vision, zero handoff gaps.
        </p>
        <div class="steps">
          <article class="step">
            <span class="step-number">1</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Strategy</h3>
              <p>We define your architecture, user journeys, and module requirements before writing a line of code.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="step">
            <span class="step-number">2</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Design & Build</h3>
              <p>Design system, content structure, and engineering delivered as one seamless, integrated package.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="step">
            <span class="step-number">3</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Launch & Optimise</h3>
              <p>We ship with confidence, train your team, and iterate based on real-world performance data.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Bluesky -->
  <section class="section tight">
    <div class="container reveal">
      <div class="surface soft pad">
        <span class="kicker">Why Bluesky?</span>
        <h2 class="title">Because your mission deserves a platform that matches its ambition</h2>
        <p class="copy">
          Most organisations end up with a website from one provider, an app from another, a handful
          of plugins, and a spreadsheet stitching it all together. That's not a platform — that's a liability.
        </p>
        <p class="copy">
          Bluesky replaces all of that with one unified system. Your website and app share a single
          content layer, one dashboard, and one set of modules. Your team updates once and publishes
          everywhere. Simple, reliable, done.
        </p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book a discovery call</a>
          <a class="btn-ghost" href="/services">Explore our services</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>
